data.message: I'm Dane cable I don't know if you remember me but we met at Kylie Jenner house she introduce me to you and we talked a lot about my trip to America I even got beat up in front of you by Kevin I don't know if you read this But I would really like to talk to you about what happened if you could give me your email or something get in contact with you I would really appreciate it please respond to my message
